LeaderboardListRequest
description: List all available leaderboards.

name: LeaderboardGetRequest
description: Get a leaderboard, along with some subset of its entries.

params.name: leaderboardId
params.description: The leaderboard ID to get data for.

name: offset
description:
Set an offset to shift the 'page' of returned entries start point. Optional.
Default 0 (first page). Must be greater than or equal to 0

params.name: offset
params.description: The offset value to use, default 0, must be greater than or equal to 0.

return.description: Current instance of this object, can be used to chain function calls.

name: limit
description:
Set a 'page' size limit for returned entries. Optional.
Default 50. Must be between 10 and 50, inclusive.

params.name: limit
params.description: The limit size to use, default 50, must be between 10 and 50, inclusive.

return.description: Current instance of this object, can be used to chain function calls.

name: withScoretags
description:
Indicate that the entries contained in the leaderboard response should include their attached
scoretags, if any are present.

return.description: Current instance of this object, can be used to chain function calls.

name: LeaderboardAndRankGetRequest
description: Get a leaderboard, along with some subset of its entries, and the rank information for the current account.

params.name: session
params.description: Session identifying the account making this request.

params.name: leaderboardId
params.description: The leaderboard ID to get data for.

name: autoOffset
description:
Indicate that the entries 'page' contained in the leaderboard response should be 'scrolled' to
contain the current account. Equivalent to autoOffset(true)

return.description: Current instance of this object, can be used to chain function calls.

params.name: session

params.name: The
params.description: key to delete the corresponding 'public' segment value for.

name: SharedStorageSearchRequest
description: Run a query over Shared Storage data.

params.name: session
params.description: Session identifying the account making this request.

params.name: query
params.description: The query string to execute.

name: filterKey
description:
Restrict the query to run only over Shared Storage keys with the given name. Defaults to no filter,
the query will run over all Shared Storage records.

params.name: key
params.description: The key filter to use.

return.description: Current instance of this object, can be used to chain function calls.

name: sort
description: Define a sort order for the results. Defaults to no sort, natural ordering is used.

params.name: key
params.description: The sort order definition to use.

return.description: Current instance of this object, can be used to chain function calls.

name: offset
description:
Offset query results by the given number of entries. Useful for paginating query results.
Default 0 (first page). Must be greater than or equal to 0.

params.name: offset
params.description: The query result offset to use.

return.description: Current instance of this object, can be used to chain function calls.

name: limit
description:
Limit the number of results returned in a single response. Must be between 0 and 100, inclusive. Default 10.
Using a limit of 0 will return no results, but can be useful for aggregation or similar scenarios
where the result count is useful by itself.

params.name: limit
params.description: The maximum number of results to return in a response.

return.description: Current instance of this object, can be used to chain function calls.
